    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You just need to filter the cars that have a <code>null</code> name:</p>\n\n<pre><code>requiredCars = cars.stream()\n                   .filter(c -&gt; c.getName() != null)\n                   .filter(c -&gt; c.getName().startsWith(\"M\"));\n</code></pre>\n"
