    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Leveraging the power of <code>java.util.Optional#map()</code>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>List&lt;Car&gt; requiredCars = cars.stream()\n  .filter (car -&gt; \n    Optional.ofNullable(car)\n      .map(Car::getName)\n      .map(name -&gt; name.startsWith(\"M\"))\n      .orElse(false) // what to do if either car or getName() yields null? false will filter out the element\n    )\n  .collect(Collectors.toList())\n;\n</code></pre>\n"
